data.description: Price reduced for immediate sale........Make an offer!This is a very desirable Harlan Ranch Leo Wilson affordable home with a well designed floorplan in outstanding condition. There are loads of upgrades to enjoy including shutters, calming paint colors, beautiful chandelier and a lovely appointed kitchen with granite countertops, deluxe backsplash with decorative accents, tiled floors, two pantries, a builtin gas cooktop and a very convenient breakfast bar plus a large dining area for all your needs. The main bedroom and bathroom  are spacious and with a  lovely countertop and shower for your relaxation and enjoyment.  The other two bedrooms are separated with easy access to the convenient laundry roomnearby. The spacious backyard is lovely with loads of lilac trees, Italian cypress, forty rose bushes (with names to be provided) and fruitless plums. Included is the relaxing covered approx. 10x10 gazebo. There are no neighbors to the rear plus a lovely bike path too. This home has a larger driveway and is part of a nearby culdesac. Easy to show. You will love your new home!
